  "name": "Wardbreaker (The Worldwound)",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/environment/settlement/watchtower-city.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl428_LabelType\">You have studied techniques designed to pierce magical protections, with the goal of assisting your Abyssal masters in bringing down the wardstones that guard the borders of Mendev.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl428_LabelType\">The Worldwound</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl428_LabelType\">Once per day, you can attempt a melee touch attack against an opponent that you believe has a deflection bonus to AC. If your attack is successful, your foe&rsquo;s deflection bonus to AC is halved (to a minimum of +0) for a number of rounds equal to your Charisma modifier. You can use this ability twice per day at 10th level and three times per day at 20th level.</span></p>",
